Package: scDIFtest
Type: Package
Title: Item-Wise Score-Based DIF Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dries", "Debeer", email = "debeer.dries@gmail.com", 
    role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: This R-package can be used for item-wise DIF tests for fitted
            'mirt', 'multipleGroup' or 'bfactor' models. Under the hood the 
            'sctest' from the 'strucchange'-package is used.
Imports: sandwich, 
         strucchange, 
